' ==== روابط include ====
UC20 ..> UC21 : <<include>>
UC10 ..> UC11 : <<include>>
UC10 ..> UC12 : <<include>>
UC29 ..> UC30 : <<include>>
UC02 ..> UC01 : <<include>>
UC24 ..> UC11 : <<include>>

' ==== روابط extend ====
UC03 ..> UC01 : <<extend>>
UC27 ..> UC19 : <<extend>>
UC23 ..> UC22 : <<extend>>
UC16 ..> UC08 : <<extend>>
UC27 ..> UC26 : <<extend>>

legend right
  <<include>> : پایه ..> واردشده (UCbase ..> UCincluded)
  <<extend>> : گسترش‌دهنده ..> پایه (UCext ..> UCbase)
endlegend

